text: Dinkelscherben (Swabian: Dinggelscherba) is a municipality in the district of Augsburg in Bavaria in Germany. Fleinhausen, Anried, Breitenbronn, Ettelried, Grünenbaindt, Häder, Lindach, Oberschöneberg and Ried are villages that make up the municipality of Dinkelscherben. ==References== Category:Augsburg (district)
title: Dinkelscherben
